<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Welcome to Tracksy</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: "Segoe UI", Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        background-color: #f5f5f5;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        color: #333;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 30px auto;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 16px;
        box-shadow: 0 5px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        overflow: hidden;
      }
      .header {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #111827, #1e3a8a);
        text-align: center;
        padding: 40px 20px;
        color: #fff;
      }
      .header h1 {
        margin: 0;
        font-size: 28px;
        letter-spacing: 1px;
      }
      .content {
        padding: 30px 25px;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .content img {
        width: 120px;
        height: 120px;
        border-radius: 50%;
        object-fit: cover;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
        border: 3px solid #1e3a8a;
      }
      .content h2 {
        font-size: 22px;
        color: #1e3a8a;
        margin-bottom: 5px;
      }
      .content p {
        font-size: 16px;
        color: #555;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }
      .user-info {
        background-color: #f3f4f6;
        padding: 15px;
        border-radius: 12px;
        margin-bottom: 25px;
        text-align: left;
      }
      .user-info p {
        margin: 5px 0;
        font-size: 15px;
      }
      .btn {
        display: inline-block;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #657cb9, #4461a1);
        color: #ffff;
        padding: 12px 25px;
        border-radius: 25px;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: 600;
        transition: background 0.3s;
      }
      .btn:hover {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3060c9, #2559e7);
      }
      .footer {
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 13px;
        color: #777;
        padding: 20px;
        border-top: 1px solid #eee;
        background-color: #fafafa;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <h1>Welcome to <strong>Tracksy</strong> ðŸš—</h1>
        <p>Your journey begins here!</p>
      </div>
      <div class="content">
        <img src="<%= profilePic %>" alt="User Profile" />
        <h2>Hello, <%= name %>!</h2>
        <p>
          Weâ€™re thrilled to have you on board with <b>Tracksy</b> â€” your trusted
          ride-sharing partner. Whether you're heading to work, a meeting, or a
          night out, Tracksy ensures your ride is safe, fast, and comfortable.
        </p>
        <div class="user-info">
          <p><strong>Name:</strong> <%= name %></p>
          <p><strong>Email:</strong> <%= email %></p>
        </div>
        <a href="<%= verifyLink %>" class="btn">Verify</a>
      </div>
      <div class="footer">
        <p>Â© <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Tracksy. All rights reserved.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
